## POST Request

**Add credentials** for the MagicHour.ai and  the make sure the body content has the JSON in following format;

```
{
  "name": "<String>",
  "image_count": <Number>,
  "orientation": "<String>",
  "style": {
    "prompt": "<String>",
    "tool": "<String>"
  }
}
```

